Package: SAGITemplates
Type: Package
Title: Add SAGI Templates to `New Rmarkdown` Window
Version: 0.1.5
Authors@R: c(
    person("Sam", "Rogers", email = "s.rogers@adelaide.edu.au", role = "aut"),
    person("Julian", "Taylor", email = "julian.taylor@adelaide.edu.au", role = "cre"))
Description: Clicking the RStudio New Rmarkdown button shows a window
    where various Rmarkdown templates can be selected. This package adds
	  SAGI-III reporting templates in this window as an easy way to 
	  add required template files such as logos, styling and initialisation scripts 
	  when creating a new report.
Imports: rmarkdown, knitr
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
